Electricity Billing System
A web-based billing system built with HTML, CSS, PHP, and MySQL that manages electricity billing for three user roles.

Key Files
main.html – Homepage with role selection

admin.html – Admin dashboard

employee.html – Employee interface

customer_login.php – Customer login

ele1.php – Add new customer (Admin)

bill.php – Generate bill (Employee)

pay.php – Payment page (Customer)

style.css – Styling for all pages

user.sql – Database schema and sample data

User Roles:
Admin – Add customers

Employee – Enter meter readings & generate bills

Customer – View and pay bills